{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "失路人", "storyInfo": "城中死傷慘重，恨火已被完全點燃，拉芙希妮與前來送葬的布莉吉結伴回城。遺跡裡，守靈人與莫蘭談論塔拉的過去。酒館中，陌生的女性接手講述故事。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您送我送得夠遠，這裡已經是守靈人的聚落了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你姐姐喚醒了我，如果你覺得我聒噪，自然也可以一把火送我回去接著睡。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_carriagegoaway"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處，金髮佩洛從馱獸背上一躍而下，向紅龍所在的方向疾奔而來。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她身後以馱獸所拖曳的是一輛臨時拼湊的板車，上面排布堆疊著長長的木箱。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——布莉吉？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼來了這裡？你身後拖著的那些是——", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……棺材？！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，棺材。涅梅絲讓我帶著這些棺材來找守靈人。他們還在遺跡裡面嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍，你身邊是不是站著什麼人？我聞到了熟悉的燒焦味，剛剛好像還聽見你和人說話——", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "“放逐王”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1690_1#2$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，只有我一個。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死了的人。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕你拉住他的手，他也拚了命要把肩膀扯脫臼，好用牙去咬他臆想中的仇人的傢伙，或是被他們撕成碎片的倒楣鬼。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有提奧，涅梅絲最終還是找到了他，他……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像事情自然而然地到了這一步，夏末節的夜晚就要到來，篝火馬上就要燒到最旺了一樣……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍抬頭朝納斯爾紗所在的方向望去。此刻遠遠地竟也能看見一個渺茫的影，勾勒出屬於紫火燃燒的輪廓。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再這樣下去，可能很快連棺材都不夠城裡用了。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願布莉吉已經到了城外……但願林中沒那麼多霧，布莉吉能從小路離開……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，這些沒用到的武器還堆在庫林屋內，不能被人看見。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個……這個是沒用光的燃料……爆炸物？也許拉芙希妮殿下回來時能用得到。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不用，堡壘中所有的僕役也都染上了紫火，而且那條貪婪的紅龍早就把他們遣散了……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡直就像……等著拉芙希妮殿下回來和她做個了斷一樣。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者……陷阱？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……羅里？你來幹嘛？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……涅梅絲。", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，是我。我在整理庫林的遺物，如果你沒事就先離開——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叛徒。", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你瘋了？！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，對，你瘋了，我們大家都瘋了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叛徒——", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是……下不了死手，明明大家都已經和死人差不多了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，哈哈……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得先把這個傢伙拖回他自己的家，別引人注意……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g1_citystreets_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲？", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒事的話，我先走了。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你手裡拿著什麼？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼，我走了。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是尼亞爾送艾瑪的項鍊，對不對？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——我已經把麵包給她了！這種時候，麵包比項鍊還重要吧！她自願給我的！", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她自願的嗎？這條項鍊她一直都戴在脖子上——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不關你的事！", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲？我還以為城裡的深池一個不剩都消失了，原來你留下來了啊！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也變成那種不會說話、不會走路，只會在原地待著的人了嗎？", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快了。你提那些人做什麼？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚就要開始慶祝夏末節了，我去消失的那些人家裡看了一圈，他們那裡剩下不少好東西，剛好晚上開宴會可以用！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……夏末節？宴會？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林的事——呃，畢竟他那個時候已經油盡燈枯了，我也不是……", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們別說這些了。看，這麼多東西，夠讓許多人盡興了！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前的人向涅梅絲打開手裡的袋子，裡面是一瓶已經結塊的瘤奶、幾個發芽許久的馬鈴薯還有幾根光禿禿的骨頭。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等著我，涅梅絲，還有庫林，我們一定能有一個最好的夏末節……", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到對方的身影消失在街道轉角，涅梅絲才想起來，這個人原本是納斯爾紗附近的鄉民。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩年前，維多利亞人以搜查深池為名抓走了她父親的那一天，她正在準備秋收之後的豐收慶典。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論拉芙希妮對城中可能出現的亂象有過怎樣程度的預料，眼下聽到的轉達都已經超出她的想像。"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須現在就回去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我一下，我把這些人送到守靈人那裡之後，就跟你一起回去。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布莉吉，你確定嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內現在已經很危險了，如果我最終失敗，那裡很可能……無人生還。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對，但我得回去。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為以前不是這樣的。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前，城裡人也缺少吃穿，但我把信遞給他們的時候，他們會為我準備一杯水。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們確實不把我當自己人，但當我講遊牧民的傳說給他們聽時，他們不會冷哼一聲走開，而是認真地聽。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們更不會像這幾天一樣……撕咬、毆打，就像故事裡的那些被喚醒的死人一樣。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果城市真的死了，遊牧民又要送信給誰呢？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#7$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g5_remains_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從納斯爾紗來的第二批遺體已經抵達，我該去做準備了。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "照這樣下去，很快還會有第三批、第四批……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我們真的什麼也不做嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過了，守靈人不會主動偏向任何一方，不會自己做出選擇。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "納斯爾紗人不是塔拉人嗎？為什麼在那座塔拉人的城市正在急速走向崩毀的時候，我們要袖手旁觀？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們隨紅龍歸來，你們擔憂她回去，會重蹈拉布雷德的覆轍。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#3$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們正是把拉布雷德送上絕路的人。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的祖先是塔拉王城內掌管典禮的祭司。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將拉布雷德迎回王城的諸般事宜，正是在艾里爾不置可否的情況下，由被拉布雷德感動的祖先擅自操辦的。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#3$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉布雷德死後，祖先們在七日之後為他還火，這才平息了塔拉原野上蔓延的死火。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而為了永遠不忘記這段慘痛的教訓，祖先們自願離開王城，搬到拉布雷德曾經的牧場自我放逐，從此才有了守靈人。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我很抱歉。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但葦草不是拉布雷德，歷史也不是永恆的循環。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果歷史真的只是循環，葦草早就已經死在了納斯爾紗的堡壘之中。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，她的姐姐，那位目空一切的領袖，她不也帶領塔拉擺脫了維多利亞的統治嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們的命運大多相似，但其中總會有決定性的不同。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“人們的命運大多相似，但其中總會有決定性的不同。”", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，您該把這句話印在書腰上，當作登上暢銷榜第一的宣傳語。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，前提是您先來把這個故事完完整整地寫下來。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來都沒有想以此牟利。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算不為金錢，您也能以此收穫相當的名聲。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個故事的基底……發生的地點……這一切……都注定了，它不是一個能讓我來流傳散布的故事。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，然後呢？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這正是我想問您的啊。然後呢？拉芙希妮回去了嗎？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡開始，我看見的、我相信的、我說出口的，彼此全都背道而馳。所以，我才失去了那些故事的結局。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是做得到，那還是你來吧，為這場鏡中人和紅龍的舞填上一個你喜歡的結局。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？我來講述也一樣嗎？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，當然，女士，如你所願——", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家舉起酒杯，搖晃著已經少了一大半的苦啤酒，和對面的女人碰了個杯。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他再度嚥下苦澀，同時心不在焉地等待不存在的回甘。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我嚇到您了嗎？您突然變得有些客氣，倒是令我覺得是自己的追問不合時宜了。", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。只是我需要告訴你，先前我們所說的一切都只是無關緊要的閒話，你能明白的，對嗎？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的女性端坐著，一言不發。作家只能從陰影中努力去辨認對方是否依然面帶微笑。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在等什麼？我這杯酒就要喝完了。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我陷入了和您一樣的問題。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您的素材和創作到此為止，我又怎麼可能把紅龍最終的命運落在紙上呢？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能說出口的就這麼多。我拒絕用完全杜撰的內容去為這個故事填上一個連我自己都說服不了的結尾，即使這樣會讓它缺乏結局。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你也沒頭緒，就也別在此逗留了。早點離開吧。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是您不瞭解、記不清，還是您寧願自己從未瞭解，從未看清過？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——什麼？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#3$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是什麼意思？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其說“失去結局”，倒不如說太多的“創作”迷暈了您自己的眼睛。需要我從頭數下來嗎？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "財寶將人們誘入黑暗。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨自將雕像拖上廣場的庫林。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有和林中黑霧相關的幾乎一切，從受拒的布莉吉、自己回城的糧車、迷路的拉芙希妮，再到城中的校官和愛布拉娜。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這些“創作”讓您腦海中的一切自相矛盾，那我的確有責任引領它們通往結局的路。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來換我為您提供自己的所見所聞，怎麼樣？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然不說話，我就當作您同意了。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願我補充的這些，能讓您找到自己滿意的結局。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}